reviewText: She's funnier in her Miranda show. I never finished this :(

Miranda Hart is terrific and this concert is very funny and well filmed! Got this for my friend who is a HUGE Miranda fan. She loves it and has watched it twice already! Also, got this as the first disc to test my new all region blu-ray player. Success!
Excellent live show.  If you like the t.v. series, this is definitely worth watching.
She was very funny but I don't think the jokes would make sense to anyone not already a fan who saw her TV series.
Miranda Hart is a great comedian.  I think anyone would like this, but I especially liked it after seeing her in her TV show Miranda.  Such fun!
Watching this DVD I could see how very popular Miranda Hart is in the UK; the venue was packed!
